name: Flying over it
description: To be honest, I don't know what to put here, you use the arrow keys to move. This was a "quick" game I felt like making to challenge myself, if it feels cut short, it's because I could no longer challenge myself, I was only making simple 3d models, and my specialty is more of coding.  It might not be as grand, or as long as getting over it which I will admit I was using as reference, but it's cool I guess. I cut this short as I could no longer challenge myself with low poly models and a tiny bit of playmaker code. If people like this for some reason, then I might add more to it, but for now, this is what I've got.
